      "updated": 1776092419
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0503ed60e6000000c7f2a4",
      "text": "2026年 28.49％経過",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776092419,
      "updated": 1776092419
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0503ed60e600000087d341",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776092419,
      "updated": 1776092419
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0e631280f00000000e2a63",
      "text": "今日のn年前",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1776094820,
      "updated": 1776094820
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0e631280f00000004d9bba",
      "text": " [2025/04/14]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1776094820,
      "updated": 1776094820
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0e631280f00000003ea321",
      "text": " [2024/04/14]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1776094820,
      "updated": 1776094820
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0e631280f0000000067026",
      "text": " [2023/04/14]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1776094820,
      "updated": 1776094820
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0e631280f00000000ffc07",
      "text": " [2022/04/14]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1776094820,
      "updated": 1776094820
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0e631280f00000009a2035",
      "text": " [2021/04/14]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1776094820,
      "updated": 1776094820
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0e631280f0000000d6b817",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1776094820,
      "updated": 1776094820
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0503ed60e600000018d9f2",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776092419,
      "updated": 1776092498
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd055200000000001d583e",
      "text": " 何があろうと此れを維持するために継続的な努力をせねばならないという物",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776092499,
      "updated": 1776092736
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd073700000000001d5840",
      "text": "   不断の努力にすると思い詰めて破綻する本末転倒な展開になるので却下",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776092983,
      "updated": 1776093058
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd06a800000000001d583f",
      "text": "  仰々しい割に結構ありそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776092840,
      "updated": 1776092911
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd079500000000001d5841",
      "text": "   ここで何をあげるのかで価値観の違いというものが良い感じに出そう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776093078,
      "updated": 1776093479
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0c030000000000cb8cda",
      "text": "  筋肉、人間関係、あと1こなんだろ、平和？[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1776094211,
      "updated": 1776094241
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0f8f0000000000728f7b",
      "text": "  (居れば)配偶者と子の生命、(居れば)配偶者と子の尊厳、自己の生命、自己の尊厳[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776095120,
      "updated": 1776095481
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd101f0000000000728f7c",
      "text": "  \t愛が重い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776095264,
      "updated": 1776095267
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd11a40000000000728f7d",
      "text": "  \t筋肉との温度差が面白い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776095652,
      "updated": 1776095660
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd12c5000000000099b960",
      "text": " 大抵の国旗は9色で塗り分けられる説というのを見かけた。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776095942,
      "updated": 1776095996
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd136a000000000099b961",
      "text": " \t白、黒、茶、赤、橙、黄、緑、水、青",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776096107,
      "updated": 1776096148
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd13ae000000000099b962",
      "text": " \t\t水色と青色の違いのような、色の境目をどう認識しているのかの話が少しありそう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776096175,
      "updated": 1776096310
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd1449000000000099b963",
      "text": " \t\t色空間上の点の分布をクラスタにすれば良いかも",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776096330,
      "updated": 1776096444
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd1467000000000099b964",
      "text": " \t\tしかしその前に色空間上に点を配置できる程国旗の色は厳密には定められていない",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776096360,
      "updated": 1776096417
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd1495000000000099b965",
      "text": " \t\tならば法律条文から色名を抽出すれば良いかも",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776096406,
      "updated": 1776096448
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0503ed60e6000000a16a39",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776092419,
      "updated": 1776092419
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0b6a0000000000cb8cd6",
      "text": "[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1776094058,
      "updated": 1776094060
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0b6b0000000000cb8cd7",
      "text": " バンタンのワルツ、今回のアルバム曲がかなり今までと違う感じの雰囲気になっていて既存の曲が浮いちゃうので馴染ませるためにほとんどの既存曲にアレンジが入っていて最高に良い",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1776094060,
      "updated": 1776094167
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd0bc00000000000cb8cd8",
      "text": "  このアレンジ集めたアルバム出して欲しい",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1776094144,
      "updated": 1776094158
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd1a8c000000000057675e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "687cfb4384cbd5c469536056",
      "created": 1776097933,
      "updated": 1776097933
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd1a8c0000000000576760",
      "text": "[salt-A.icon]",
      "userId": "687cfb4384cbd5c469536056",
      "created": 1776097933,
      "updated": 1776097937
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd1a910000000000576761",
      "text": " 新規更新を追うのが楽しい",
      "userId": "687cfb4384cbd5c469536056",
      "created": 1776097937,
      "updated": 1776097978
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd1aba0000000000576762",
      "text": " 　[2 hop link]から色んな所に飛べるのが楽しい",
      "userId": "687cfb4384cbd5c469536056",
      "created": 1776097978,
      "updated": 1776098009
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd1ba10000000000576769",
      "text": " 　開けるなら24時間開いてしまう気がする",
      "userId": "687cfb4384cbd5c469536056",
      "created": 1776098210,
      "updated": 1776098219
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd1ad80000000000576763",
      "text": "　[YMM4]",
      "userId": "687cfb4384cbd5c469536056",
      "created": 1776098009,
      "updated": 1776098054
    },
